{"tid":1863864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港共 : 醫護未夠班同特首直接對話 訴求與人流措施如同一轍","createTime":"2020-02-05T10:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T11:26:39.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"114e59c143f72e6be9215c5ad057f7f48e0d8ee2","tid":1863864,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥指工會訴求應由醫管局高層處理<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，發起工業行動的醫管局員工陣線，多次邀約下，她都未有出席會面，是因為認為有關問題是機構人事管理議題，由醫管局主席或行政總裁會見最適合，亦會向她反映意見。她又認為，工會爭取的目標和政府並無大分歧，政府一直採取措施希望減少跨境人流，同時已多次表明，將醫護對防疫物資的需求放在首位。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又指，雖然未能精準估計有多少入境人士需要接強制檢疫，但過去關閉口岸後，入境人次已減至不足兩成，相信實施強制檢疫後，亦不會處理太大量人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1259544&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1259544%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2FE8yPsxO6SBEJdrny20pcfhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=c4369986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1259544&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"7968d958ad1e92eac37dcc38bd143c54aeb0955e","tid":1863864,"uid":222907,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"政府已經唔care罷工班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ef4393d07079e8705560073de0f31a68e240b2","tid":1863864,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7968d958ad1e92eac37dcc38bd143c54aeb0955e","tid":1863864,"uid":222907,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"政府已經唔care罷工班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講一套做一套"},{"pid":"d5f78e4f1ee454fa01757c567bafa36e11d6bce4","tid":18